lead_paragraph: Two outsize egos are sparring over a Chicago landmark, with Mayor Rahm Emanuel complaining that Donald Trump has put an "architecturally tasteless" sign on the city's second-tallest building - a display of giant letters spelling out the real estate tycoon's name.

headline.main: Chicago Mayor Emanuel Terms Trump's Tower Sign 'Tasteless'
headline.print_headline: Chicago Mayor Emanuel Terms Trump's Tower Sign 'Tasteless'
